# Recall Mobile (Expo)

- Functional components + hooks only
- Network calls only through `lib/api.ts` — never call LLM providers from mobile
- Use product model aliases, never provider names
- Google Sign-In requires dev build; Expo Go uses dev auth placeholder
- Physical device: `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` must be Mac LAN IP, not localhost
